title: Toni Garrn
summary: Antonia Garrn (German pronunciation: [ˈtoːni ˈɡaʁn]; born 7 July 1992) is a German model. She rose to prominence in the fashion industry after signing an exclusive contract with Calvin Klein in 2008.In October 2020, Garrn married British actor Alex Pettyfer. Their daughter was born in 2021.
